Code.Other:
1. 打开 AWS 控制台并前往 VPC > Endpoints
2. 选择该 endpoint，然后依次选择 Actions > Manage policy
3. 选择 Custom 并粘贴此最小策略，将其替换为你信任的账户 ID：
   ```json
   {
     "Version": "2012-10-17",
     "Statement": [
       {
         "Effect": "Allow",
         "Principal": "*",
         "Action": "*",
         "Resource": "*",
         "Condition": {
           "StringEquals": {
             "aws:PrincipalAccount": [
               "<TRUSTED_ACCOUNT_ID_1>",
               "<TRUSTED_ACCOUNT_ID_2>"
             ]
           }
         }
       }
     ]
   }
   ```
4. 点击 Save

Code.Terraform:
```hcl
#将此添加到现有的 VPC 端点资源中以限制访问
resource "aws_vpc_endpoint" "<example_resource_name>" {
  #...该端点现有的必需参数...

  policy = jsonencode({
    Version = "2012-10-17"
    Statement = [{
      Effect    = "Allow"
      Principal = "*"
      Action    = "*"
      Resource  = "*"
      Condition = {                       #关键：按受信任的账户进行限制
        StringEquals = {
          "aws:PrincipalAccount" = [      #关键：只有这些账户可以使用该端点
            "<TRUSTED_ACCOUNT_ID_1>",
            "<TRUSTED_ACCOUNT_ID_2>"
          ]
        }
      }
    }]
  })
}
```
